_:Nd200195aa6d64783b3aff3e9434cf293 <http://schema.org/name> "Air Vice-Marshal Peter Squires OBE MA BEng(Hons)" .
_:Nd200195aa6d64783b3aff3e9434cf293 <http://schema.org/description> "<ul>\n  <li>Administrator of the Sovereign Base Areas of Akrotiri and Dhekelia and Commander British Forces Cyprus</li>\n  <li>Head of Defence Operational Capability, providing impartial assessments to Ministers and Service Chiefs</li>\n  <li>Commandant of the Royal Air Force College Cranwell, overseeing all initial officer and aviator training, Tedder Academy of Leadership, RAF’s Youth Engagement and STEM Policy, and University Air Squadrons</li>\n  <li>Head of Approvals Division, Military Aviation Authority</li>\n  <li>Commander of the Expeditionary Air Wing during Operation UNIFIED PROTECTOR in Libya</li>\n  <li>Director Defence Studies for the RAF</li>\n  <li>Command of 100 Squadron</li>\n</ul>\n" .
